fulltitle: Jazz/Groove Drum Instruction: Jack McDuff Style / Hammond B-3 Organ Combo
title: Jazz/Groove Drum Instruction: Jack McDuff Style / Hammond B-3 Organ Combo
description:
From an unreleased instructional video I did ages ago.

Rudy Petschauer was Jack McDuff's drummer for over 10 years and recorded on many of his last CDs.
On the video we have a discussion about what makes the organ groove so unique, and Rudy talks about (and demonstrates!) some of the tips given to him by Jack McDuff.   

Video also features myself, guitarist Royce Campbell and tenor titan monster Jerry Weldon.
